{"tid":1474492,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"嘩屌你老母 連儂牆係咁揼個靚仔都係守行為","createTime":"2019-08-15T07:54:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T09:10:11.000Z","uid":2748,"like":39,"dislike":94,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"4835df6ceba9aa6d0fc8cdc7d8cfd7ef4eb23d54","tid":1474492,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:54:25.000Z","msg":"報稱商人的男子，在九龍灣「連儂牆」觀看字條時，見一名六旬男子欲撕去牆上的便條紙，於是上前阻止，二人因而起爭執，商人腳踢六旬翁腹部一下，被控普通襲擊罪，案件今（15日）在觀法院再提訊，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">控方決定撤銷控罪，商人准以1000元簽保守行為1年</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n報稱商人的被告，原被控在本年7月11日，在觀塘道九龍灣巴士站，襲擊事主周惠祥。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，被告當時正在旁看「連儂牆」的內容，事主周惠祥在返家途中亦途經該處，周認為他人不應在此處張貼紙張，故撕去紙張，被告上前阻止，二人繼而發生爭執，被告期間腳踢周的腹部一下，有途人見狀報警。被告在警誡下稱一時衝動才干犯罪行。"},{"pid":"c18455e026b6e045ef22ef694a66fffd24cf15d1","tid":1474492,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f36f42e404f85f3c0396ab078ff50b77f71460e","tid":1474492,"uid":44674,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:55:24.000Z","msg":"題與文不符"},{"pid":"b552f2fc861fbadf2c0dcbde8e18cd5abc435aa3","tid":1474492,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https:/